        <num>138.450</num>
        <content>
          <p>As used in  to  unless the context requires otherwise:</p>
          <p>means the total consideration given, as determined in ;</p>
          <p>means the total consideration given, excluding any amount allowed as a trade-in allowance by the seller, as attested to in a notarized affidavit, provided that the retail price established by the notarized affidavit shall not be less than fifty percent (50%) of the difference between the trade-in value, as established by the reference manual, of the motor vehicle offered for registration and the trade-in value, as established by the reference manual, of any motor vehicle offered in trade as part of the total consideration given.</p>
